<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="">
  <head>
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
  </head>

  <style>
    #drop {
      font-family: NotoSansKR-Regular;
      margin: 20px auto;
      border: 1px solid #8080805c;
      padding: 12px 5px;
      width: 40%;
      float: left;
      color: #5172df;
      widows: 100%;
    }

    #etc {
      font-family: NotoSansKR-Regular;
      margin: 20px auto;
      border: 1px solid #8080805c;
      padding: 12px 5px;
      width: 100%;
      float: left;
      color: #5172df;
      widows: 100%;
      height: 300;
    }

    .info {
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: red;
    }

    label {
      padding: 4px 2px;
      width: 100%;
    }
    input[type="submit"],
    input[type="dropuser"] {
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid #8080805c;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 5px;
      background-color: #5172df;
      color: white;
      cursor: pointer;
      margin-top : 36%;
    }

    input[name="dropuser"] {
      width: 20%;
      float: left;
    }

    .content {
      width: 66%;
      float: left;
    }
    .profile {
      width: 100%;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .image {
      margin: 20px auto;
      width: 25%;
      height: 25%;
      float: right;
      margin-right: 15%;
    }

    .button {
      margin: 0 auto;
      width: 100%;
    }

    h5{
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .container{
    padding : 50px;
    min-width:  70%;
    background-color: white;
  }

  .row3{       
    background-color: #f8f8f8;    
  }
  </style>

  <body id="top">
    <!-- Top Background Image Wrapper -->
    <div
      class="bgded overlay"
      style="background-image: url('/images/child.jpg')"
    >
      <%- include('../partials/nav') %>

      <div id="breadcrumb" class="hoc clear">
        <h6 class="heading" style="font-family: NotoSansKR-Regular;">마이 페이지</h6>
        <br />
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/index">메인</a></li>
          <li><a href="/mypage/account">마이 페이지</a></li>
          <li><a href="/mypage/delete">회원 탈퇴</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- End Top Background Image Wrapper -->
    <div class="wrapper row3">
      <main class="hoc container clear">
        <!--네비게이션-->
        <%- include('mypage_nav') %>
        <!--본 문-->
        <div class="content three_quarter">
          <h2 style="font-family: NotoSansKR-Regular">
            회원탈퇴
          </h2>
          <form action="/mypage/delete" method="post">
            <div class="profile">
              <div class="one_two">
                <label class="info" for="info">* 회원탈퇴사유</label>
                <h5
                  style="
                    text-align: left;
                    font-family: NotoSansKR-Regular;
                  "
                >
                  그동안 키즈가든과 함께해 주셔서 감사합니다. 탈퇴 사유를 남겨
                  주시면 향후 서비스 개선에 적극적으로 반영하겠습니다.
                </h5>
                <label for="drop">사유 선택</label>
                <select name="drop" id="drop">
                  <option value>사유를 선택해주세요</option>
                  <option value="service1">
                    아이가 졸업하여, 서비스를 이용할 일이 없어서
                  </option>
                  <option value="service2">서비스 이용이 불편해서</option>
                  <option value="service3">원하는 기능을 지원하지 않아서</option>
                  <option value="service4">기타 의견</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="one_two">
              <p>
                <textarea
                  name="etc"
                  id="etc"
                  cols="50"
                  rows="10"
                  placeholder="기타 의견을 작성해주세요"
                ></textarea>
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="button">
              <input type="submit" name="submit" value="탈퇴 하기" />
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="clear"></div>
      </main>
    </div>
    <%- include('../partials/foot') %> <%- include('../partials/copyright') %>
    <%- include('../partials/top') %>
  </body>
</html>
